rows.label: qev041902_MSG0001
rows.name:
What does princess like Popo see in that pauper?
Rrraaaaugh! So FRUSTRATING![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0002
rows.name:
...Hnnh? Friend has business with moneylender Jalolo?
Interest starts at 50 percent every 10 days.
Except Jalolo irritated, so make that 80 percent.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0003
rows.name:
Meh! Why should Jalolo lend someone else money to
buy present for Popo?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0004
rows.name:
...Mrrr? Human has business with moneylender Jalolo?
Jalolo willing to lend, but interest start at 100 percent
every 10 days.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_JNK0010
rows.name: Persuade

rows.label: qev041902_SEL0011
rows.name: Convince Jalolo to lend money to Nio.

rows.label: qev041902_JNK0020
rows.name: Query

rows.label: qev041902_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Jalolo what has him so upset.

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0005
rows.name:
Lending money may be job of Jalolo, but that not
mean he have to lend to useless worm like Nio.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0006
rows.name: What benefit is there for Jalolo?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0007
rows.name:
Jalolo not need to answer that! ...But he will anyway.
Worm standing next to human friend is reason![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0008
rows.name: Mira will freeze over before Jalolo lend to...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0009
rows.name: ......[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0010
rows.name: Wait. No. No, this perfect![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0011
rows.name:
All right. Jalolo changed mind.
Jalolo will take pity and lend money to Nio.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0012
rows.name: Really? Then Nio eager to sign![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0013
rows.name:
BUT! If Nio fail to pay entire sum back by specified
date, Jalolo will take every last piece of stringy hair on
head of Nio in lieu of payment.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0014
rows.name:
WHAT?! B-but tuft is pride of any Nopon!
Nio could never part with it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0015
rows.name:
Then no deal. Nio will have no present for young miss,
and failed wedding will most shameful event of year.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0016
rows.name:
Well, as soon as Ntoto arrive, Nio can pay back loan,
sooooo...all right. Nio will sign contract.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_JNK0030
rows.name: Stop

rows.label: qev041902_SEL0031
rows.name: Prevent Nio from entering into such a risky deal.

rows.label: qev041902_JNK0040
rows.name: Permit

rows.label: qev041902_SEL0041
rows.name: Let Nio make his own decisions.

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0017
rows.name:
Not to worry. Money Nio has saved can cover this,
no problem.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0018
rows.name:
Okay, here is signed contract. And if due date comes
and Nio unable to pay, Jalolo can have all this lovely,
lovely tuft hair.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0019
rows.name:
Yes, yes. Pleasure doing business. Just make sure you
come back with money, worm.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0020
rows.name:
Oh-hoooo! Now Popo can have perfect wedding dress
she deserve![ST:wait ]

rows.label: NewText_42
rows.name: Nio must hurry before they sell out![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0021
rows.name: ...Hmm? Was Nio here just now?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0022
rows.name:
Popo is fianc√©epon of Nio and have urgent news
for him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_JNK0050
rows.name: Explain

rows.label: qev041902_SEL0051
rows.name: Tell Popo everything that happened.

rows.label: qev041902_JNK0060
rows.name: Evade

rows.label: qev041902_SEL0061
rows.name:
Give Popo a vague outline of what happened,
but leave out any mention of the dress.

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0023
rows.name:
Meh-meh?! Nio borrowed money from Jalolo to buy
wedding dress?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0024
rows.name:
Ugh! That idiot picked worst possible time to
borrow money from worst possible person.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0025
rows.name: Why would Nio borrow money from Jalolo?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0026
rows.name:
Ntoto not know reason, but Nio must have thought
to pay it back with money Ntoto was bringing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041902_MSG0027
rows.name: We must stop that fool Nopon![ST:wait ]
